{"route":{"route":"/posts/95db8f9/","outputPath":"posts/95db8f9/index.html","kind":"post","title":"langchaingoでRAGを試しました","language":"ja","params":{"abbrlink":"95db8f9"}},"description":"日本語はまだ勉強中ですから、変などころあったら、ぜひコメントしてください。 RAGとは RAGはRetrieval augmented generationの略です。 大規模言語モデル内容を生成する前に、promptによる外部のデーターベースに知識を検索、元のpromptと組み合わせて、アウトプットを改善するための技術","post":{"kind":"post","sourcePath":"source/_posts/langchaingoでRAGを試しました.md","route":"/posts/95db8f9/","abbrlink":"95db8f9","title":"langchaingoでRAGを試しました","date":"2024-11-06 10:37:12","updated":"2024-11-06 10:37:12","tags":["llm","rag","text embedding"],"categories":["llm"],"language":"ja","htmlLang":"ja","locale":"ja_JP","textDirection":"ltr","dateLocale":"ja-JP","excerptMarkdown":"","excerptHtml":"","bodyMarkdown":"","bodyHtml":"<blockquote>\n<p>日本語はまだ勉強中ですから、変などころあったら、ぜひコメントしてください。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"ragとは\">RAGとは</h2>\n<p>RAGはRetrieval augmented generationの略です。<br>\n大規模言語モデル内容を生成する前に、promptによる外部のデーターベースに知識を検索、元のpromptと組み合わせて、アウトプットを改善するための技術です。</p>\n<div class=\"mermaid mermaid-pending\" data-mermaid-source=\"sequenceDiagram\n    actor ユーザ\n    ユーザ-&gt;&gt;サーバー: prompt: 今日の注目&lt;br/&gt;の新聞は何ですか？\n    サーバー-&gt;&gt;ベクトルデータベース: promptをキーワードとして&lt;br/&gt;知識を検索\n    ベクトルデータベース--)サーバー: 知識を返す\n    サーバー-&gt;&gt;llm: promptと知識を組み合わせて\n    llm--&gt;&gt;サーバー: 生成する内容を返す\n    サーバー-&gt;&gt;ユーザ: 内容を返す\n\" aria-busy=\"true\"></div><p>例えば：</p>\n<p>ユーザ：今日の注目の新聞は何ですか？</p>\n<p>gemini：</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-txt\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">今日の注目の新聞記事については、リアルタイムで変化するため、特定の新聞社名を挙げて「今日の注目の記事はこれです」と断言することは難しいです。</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>chatgpt:</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-txt\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">本日（2024年11月6日）の日本の注目ニュースは次のような内容が含まれている可能性があります：</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">アメリカ大統領選挙の最新動向 - 特に若い世代の投票行動や政策への関心が注目されています。</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">国内経済とインフレの動き - 日本の物価高騰が続き、家計への影響や政府の対応が議論されています。</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">アジアの地政学的緊張 - 日本周辺地域の安全保障に関連する動向が続いています。</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">以上の内容が注目ニュースとして考えられますが、詳細については直接ニュースソースで確認されるとよいでしょう。</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>geminiはリアルタイムによっての内容は回答できません。<br>\nchatgptはRAGか、Function Callingか、どちらかを使っていると思います。<br>\n今回はgolang+langchaingo+ollama+qdrantでRAGを実験してみます。</p>\n<h2 id=\"準備\">準備</h2>\n<h3 id=\"ollamaをインストール\">ollamaをインストール</h3>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">curl -fsSL https://ollama.com/install.sh | sh</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"qdrantのコンテナを実行\">qdrantのコンテナを実行</h3>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">mkdir</span> -p ~/.config/qdrant</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">docker run -p 6333:6333 -p 6334:6334 \\</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    -v ~/.config/qdrant:/qdrant/storage:z \\</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">    qdrant/qdrant</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"bge-large-en-v15をollamaで実行\">bge-large-en-v1.5をollamaで実行</h3>\n<p>知識をベクトルデータベースに保存するにはText Embedingモデルが必要です。今回はbge-large-en-v1.5を使うことになりました。</p>\n<p>ollamaのモデルライブラリにはbge-large-en-v1.5がありませんので、bge-large-en-v1.5をGGUFに変換することが必要です。</p>\n<p>git-lfsとcmakeをインストール</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">sudo</span> apt install git-lfs cmake</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">git lfs install</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">clone</span> https://huggingface.co/BAAI/bge-large-en-v1.5</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>llama.cppをクローン</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">git <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">clone</span> https://github.com/ggerganov/llama.cpp.git</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">cd</span> llama.cpp/</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># python仮想環境はおすすめです</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">sudo</span> apt install python3.12-venv</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">python3 -m venv python-venv</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">./python-venv/bin/pip3  install -r requirements.txt</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>GGUFに変換</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> ./llama.cpp/python-venv/bin/python3 ./llama.cpp/convert_hf_to_gguf.py ./bge-large-en-v1.5/</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">cd</span> bge-large-en-v1.5/</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">echo</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;FROM ./bge-large-en-v1.5-F16.gguf&quot;</span> &gt; Modelfile</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">ollama create bge-large-en-v1.5-F16 -f Modelfile</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># embedingモデルはollamaで直接実行はできませんです</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># Error: &quot;bge-large-en-v1.5-F16&quot; does not support generate</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># ここは試してみてだけです</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">ollama run bge-large-en-v1.5-F16</span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"qwen25をollamaで実行\">Qwen2.5をollamaで実行</h3>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 32bは20GBのGPUメモリ(VRAM)が必要です</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># CPUもできるですが、非常に重いですから</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\"># 3bや7bや14bなどもぜひ使ってみてください</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:1\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">ollama run qwen2.5:32b-instruct</span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"実現\">実現</h2>\n<h3 id=\"text-embedder\">text embedder</h3>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-go\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> (</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;github.com/tmc/langchaingo/embeddings&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;github.com/tmc/langchaingo/llms/ollama&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;github.com/tmc/langchaingo/vectorstores/qdrant&quot;</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> llm, err := ollama.New(</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  ollama.WithModel(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;bge-large-en-v1.5-F16&quot;</span>),</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  ollama.WithServerURL(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;http://localhost:11434&quot;</span>),</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> )</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">panic</span>(err)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> embeder, err := embeddings.NewEmbedder(llm)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">panic</span>(err)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">19</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">20</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">qu,err := url.Parse(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;http://localhost:6333&quot;</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">21</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">22</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">panic</span>(err)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">23</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">24</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">25</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> qd, err := qdrant.New(</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">26</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  qdrant.WithURL(*qu),</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">27</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  qdrant.WithCollectionName(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;test&quot;</span>),</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">28</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  qdrant.WithEmbedder(embeder),</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">29</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> )</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">30</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">31</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span>, err</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">32</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> }</span></span></code></pre>\n<p>テキストを導入</p>\n<pre class=\"hljs code-block\"><code class=\"language-go\"><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">1</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">2</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">// TextToChunks テキストを分割</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">3</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"hljs-title\">TextToChunks</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(r io.Reader, chunkSize, chunkOverlap <span class=\"hljs-type\">int</span>)</span></span> ([]schema.Document, <span class=\"hljs-type\">error</span>) {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">4</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 新たなドキュメンタリーローダーを作成</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">5</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> docLoaded := documentloaders.NewText(r)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">6</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// テキストを再帰的に分割し方法</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">7</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> split := textsplitter.NewRecursiveCharacter()</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">8</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 分割サイズを設定</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">9</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> split.ChunkSize = chunkSize</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">10</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// 重なるサイズを設定</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">11</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> split.ChunkOverlap = chunkOverlap</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">12</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// ロードして分割する</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">13</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> docs, err := docLoaded.LoadAndSplit(context.Background(), split)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">14</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">15</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">panic</span>(err)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">16</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">17</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">return</span> docs, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span></span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">18</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">}</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">19</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">20</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  docs, err := TextToChunks(strings.NewReader(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`テストテキスト`</span>), <span class=\"hljs-number\">300</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">20</span>)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">21</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> err != <span class=\"hljs-literal\">nil</span> {</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">22</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  <span class=\"hljs-built_in\">panic</span>(err)</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">23</span><span class=\"code-line-content\">  }</span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><span class=\"code-line-number\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"--line-digits:2\">24</span><span class=\"code-line-content\"> </span></span><span class=\"code-line\"><s